_json.gridTitle: Bakin Without Eggs Delicious Egg Free Dessert Recipes from the Heart and Kitchen of a Food Allergic Family
_json.description: Finally, delicious recipes for cookies, cakes, and other baked goods that use no eggs!Millions of people-- including 5 percent of all American children-- have a food allergy, and eggs are one of the most common culprits. In this easy-to-use collection of recipes, Rosemarie Emro presents more than one hundred crowd-pleasing desserts and other treats that contain no eggs.
